para_trans: Government Decision No: Grade 2222 / Q. No.218 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. By / Room 3 / T2
Primary Health Centre Patonda, Ta. A proposal to upgrade the 30-bed rural hospital of Amarner District Jalgaon was under the consideration of the government.
Primary Health Centre Patonda, Ta. The upgradation of Amranner, District Jalgaon to a 30-bed rural hospital is being approved as a "special case" under this Government Decision.
Separate action will be taken for the construction and post creation of a 30-bed rural hospital in this category by acquiring land in the prescribed manner.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
